  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >OVERVIEW: </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1653880/extras/a987cb64bac5279b592ffe251024e7ab.poster.avif?t=1746203219\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1653880/extras/a987cb64bac5279b592ffe251024e7ab.webm?t=1746203219\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1653880/extras/a987cb64bac5279b592ffe251024e7ab.mp4?t=1746203219\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Embark on an epic galactic conquest in Imperius, the ultimate 3D space RTS experience! Engage in explosive battles with stunning graphics, and master the intricacies of deep tactical combat mechanics!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >COMBAT:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1653880/extras/978f1dfa587f4e6c53da3ca49db9933a.poster.avif?t=1746203219\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1653880/extras/978f1dfa587f4e6c53da3ca49db9933a.webm?t=1746203219\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1653880/extras/978f1dfa587f4e6c53da3ca49db9933a.mp4?t=1746203219\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Plan your strategic odyssey with 24 units, each boasting its own special ability, and command epic hero units in riveting wave defense. Engage in single-player battles against dynamic AI opponents that adapt to your every move, providing an ever-evolving challenge. Experience the thrill as your fleet targets and demolishes specific parts of enemy ships, from turrets to engines. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >MOVEMENT:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1653880/extras/bc79e66eb90abaaf4c180011960911d6.poster.avif?t=1746203219\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1653880/extras/bc79e66eb90abaaf4c180011960911d6.webm?t=1746203219\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1653880/extras/bc79e66eb90abaaf4c180011960911d6.mp4?t=1746203219\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Command your fleet in a thrilling three-dimensional battlefield, aided by auto-pathfinding that makes asteroids and other obstacles seamless to navigate. Effortlessly arrange multiple ships into dynamic formations, and outmaneuver your opponents with advanced flanking tactics.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >MULTIPLAYER:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1653880/extras/80c6fc738a35f7780d52962222e7e25d.poster.avif?t=1746203219\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1653880/extras/80c6fc738a35f7780d52962222e7e25d.webm?t=1746203219\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1653880/extras/80c6fc738a35f7780d52962222e7e25d.mp4?t=1746203219\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Gear up for the ultimate showdown in Imperius' electrifying online multiplayer skirmish mode! Rally 2–4 players as they unleash armies and clash for survival in intense free-for-all battles or strategic team warfare. Seamlessly host or join matches with your Steam friends, and prepare for a showdown of galactic proportions!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >OVERVIEW: </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1653880/extras/a987cb64bac5279b592ffe251024e7ab.poster.avif?t=1746203219\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1653880/extras/a987cb64bac5279b592ffe251024e7ab.webm?t=1746203219\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1653880/extras/a987cb64bac5279b592ffe251024e7ab.mp4?t=1746203219\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Embark on an epic galactic conquest in Imperius, the ultimate 3D space RTS experience! Engage in explosive battles with stunning graphics, and master the intricacies of deep tactical combat mechanics!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >COMBAT:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1653880/extras/978f1dfa587f4e6c53da3ca49db9933a.poster.avif?t=1746203219\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1653880/extras/978f1dfa587f4e6c53da3ca49db9933a.webm?t=1746203219\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1653880/extras/978f1dfa587f4e6c53da3ca49db9933a.mp4?t=1746203219\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Plan your strategic odyssey with 24 units, each boasting its own special ability, and command epic hero units in riveting wave defense. Engage in single-player battles against dynamic AI opponents that adapt to your every move, providing an ever-evolving challenge. Experience the thrill as your fleet targets and demolishes specific parts of enemy ships, from turrets to engines. 